Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:33.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:36.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:40.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:42.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:44.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:47.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:50.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:01.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:09.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.39,0:01:11.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Menos appeared…\Nand he defeated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:48.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This news will eventually reach\Nthe Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:50.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,KUROSAKI CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea so early\Nin the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You had a realization or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:13.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's what your sister did!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A washing was enough,\Nbut she went and…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:17.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:21.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu must've felt sorry 'cuz\Nyou were so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:22.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She even put this ornament on my ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And she used super glue!\NIt won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:32.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes! She thinks\NI'm just a stuffed toy and…Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you doing?! Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:37.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd come off if\NI pulled hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No good. I think your ear'll come off first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the time! I'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:49.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast! Breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one who's\Nalways treated like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:03.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not a comrade?!\NAm I not an equal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll leave on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:09.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll find the one…\Nwho will be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The place where I truly belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:16.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rukia, time to leave for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down! I can hear you fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just tired from\Nyesterday's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:42.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I stormed out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:48.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no money,\Nso I can't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pick me up!\NYou're Ichigo's classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:01.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Girls can't resist picking up\Na cute stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh what a…cute stuffed animal…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Dirty stuffed animal.\N– Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Eh?\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're staring…at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It just spoke, didn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped\Nin a case like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo Kunieda,\NKarakura High School Track Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I run the 100 meters in 12 seconds flat!\NYou won't outrun me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:38.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why?!\NAll I wanted was some kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In short…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, with pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you really come early,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:04.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.\NIt's almost summer vacation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:08.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking about it and\Ncan't sleep, like, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:13.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes! Kuchiki, do you have\Nany plans for the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:20.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge Fireworks Festival\Nin August.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:23.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki and the others,\Nwe're all planning to go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Fireworks Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We should ask Kurosaki, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:34.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be like the time we all went\N to the Burarei program.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was some event, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:48.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he came along just for his family,\Nhe can be very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:54.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has such a fun family,\Nhe should lighten up a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:59.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki has a permanent frown\Non his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:04.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't care\Ntoo much for Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:05.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you take a good look at him,\Nhe has an interesting face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:16.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the\NFireworks Festival with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:39.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay come on, Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, my goddess Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Earlier was just a rehearsal.\N– Go, Orihime! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:48.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Hime! You look great!\N– The real thing starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll lie there helpless\Nin front of Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:56.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Holy Mother,\N she is sure to hold me gently,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– So cute!\N– and cuddle me in the Valley of the Gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! My target has always been Orihime!\NHer and only her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once decided, you must act quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:09.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And then, soft, warm cuddles await…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:15.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure Kill! Dragon Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't supposed to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! A one-run lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:31.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yakka = soccer and baseball\N		Orihime, I think your game of "Yakka"\N		isn't fair to the defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:35.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And a one-run lead isn't cause\Nfor a celebration yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it a day.\NFree period's over anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I was just getting warmed up!\N– What're they doing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey hey!\NYou were looking at Inoue, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...talk about well-shaped jugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get offa me!\NAnd quit babbling nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're healthy high school boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being\Ninterested in cute girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right already!\NThere's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:07.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You prefer...the Mizuiro type, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you! Quit fooling around\Nand start helping over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There! That's the last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:20.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...\NIshida hasn't come by yet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At Central Park, mumbling to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And sounding so dramatic, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– He always acts like he's in a drama.\N– This guy was nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Well, that's true, but...\N– Close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet he's in some theater group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There were some weird men\Naround him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:48.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And there was even an explosion...\Nit was pretty wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:52.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,God, thank you for making him\Nsuch an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to those injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I fell...from the stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Like, for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:20.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...well anyway, take your seat,\Nand let's continue class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Really? Is it okay?\N– Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He brought it upon himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:38.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't worry about injuries like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Who said not to worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:45.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:57.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Ishida was\Nthat late... Third period!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have lunch together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but can I invite\Nsomeone else, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? A new girl? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:18.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why Ishida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eating with a guy like that\Ncan't be fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! It must be the bandages!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Were those bandages that funny, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– No thanks!\N– So blunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:39.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon. It's Keigo's treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stingy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been suspected from\Nthe very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:00.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, come and join us for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta, get serious and sweep properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:18.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! This is the age when\Nmen are silent and play soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tessai... Kisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:44.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! If it isn't Yoruichi! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Upsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:53.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is Yoruichi and\Nit's the Boss's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh? A cat as a best friend?\N– Once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I feel sorry for the Boss sometimes.\N– Here! Up and up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:04.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I guess you could say that.\N– Upsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:18.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is such a painful lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's only you, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Keigo, say something\Nto cheer us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:51.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna get so moody,\N you shouldn't have asked Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I ate saury in Meguro recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the waiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:00.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Kurosaki, why'd you invite me?\N– I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Out of sympathy for these wounds?\N– He looked like a comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, it's misplaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:08.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't care to be pitied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:13.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I just felt like it...that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:16.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask you because I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:19.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So just be grateful I asked at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:25.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I prefer to eat alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like to be alone when I eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...\NJust look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:33.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Why should I be  the one to look away?\N– These two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're so alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All together now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:45.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tadah! Today's lunch is\NCastella sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:50.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Castella sponge cake with bean jelly\Nis the ultimate for sweets lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime, how come she can\Neat such things and not gain weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All the nutrients are going\Nto her breasts, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, do you like Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:10.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or, to put it bluntly... Just what is your\Nrelationship with Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we’re frie--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mahana, that was way too bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:19.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You're the ones\Nwho want to know, but can't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I popped the question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, not you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care for Ichigo\Nanyway, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:35.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that I don't like him.\NHis face just looks a bit scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I think he has\Nan interesting face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:43.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? When did you get over\Nyour fear of Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki is just a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Are you serious?\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:04.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't feel anything for him?\NNot at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:12.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! If you like Kurosaki,\Nthen I'd have to start liking him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Tatsuki can start liking him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:18.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and why don’t we all start liking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:22.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then it would have been\Na sure win for the girl's team!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This kid is starting her\Nnonsensical rambling again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A group competition from\Nthe start sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:34.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I want Orihime's first\Nhappy face to be all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so... Let's begin with\Na one-on-one relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ughh... That was a nice parry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a parry, it was a punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll come up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with a new concoction\Nwith bean jam...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So let's eat it together, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err... I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not the same answer again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:04.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying,\N"I'll think about it."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:14.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:21.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be treated like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:27.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! This is all Ichigo's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just wait, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the deadly weapons that\Nweird manager has collected here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:35.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and get my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're also\None of the cat family,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,don't put me in\Nthe same class as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Scared ya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good riddance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:56.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Mod Souls can\Neven enter stuffed toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:16:59.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroichi told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're that cat from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Now then... What'll we do with you?\N– Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:08.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Hey Ururu, grab his feet!\N– What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– One and two and...!\N– Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noooooooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:39.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:43.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:58.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:02.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, there's nothing\Nwrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there gonna be another\None like yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:12.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What would we do if a Menos Grande\Nappeared so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:18.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're...acting a bit strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– It's...!\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:40.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:42.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:47.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now! I realize that\Nmy place is with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You ran away? Hey you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:57.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh! The world was so cruel to\N this one who ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...I'm going back to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Going back, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:05.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:10.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. But he's really become\Nattached to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:18.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But look at you! Look,\Nyou have stuffing coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Hey! What're you doing?!\N– I'm amazed he didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:23.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Oh well, we'll take you to him.\N– Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,HANDICRAFT CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:26.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:29.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? I thought this is\Nyour specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:30.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:31.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:37.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I got it!\NCan't do a thing with those hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's impossible. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can't even thread\Na needle like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How insulting!\N These wounds are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:49.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And just watch me!\NThe work of a master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– This is a piece of cake for me!\N– What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I dunno...\N– What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:55.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's been powered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:13.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have high-grade fabric so that\NI can accept orders at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the material I used here--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:15.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just cut the crap!\NMaking fun of me and... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:23.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to run away, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Yoruichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop putting on an act, Kisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:51.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you talk about it before\Nor after your milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:57.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's dinnertime... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:03.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, she went off somewhere again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:05.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.\N                        Rukia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:14.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rear conformity 113!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:18.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Neural coefficient 88.5%.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually in a Gigai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:26.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think the data from\Nthe Visuals Department was reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
