Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:56.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:58.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:01.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:04.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:06.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:10.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:18.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:21.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:23.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:26.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:28.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:31.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:32.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:37.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ishida, president of\Nthe Handicrafts Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:39.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to say one thing...
