Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:44.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I had more time, I could've come up\Nwith a more fashionable look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:48.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time, I'll show you my work that\Nwill make your spine tingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:48.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait.
